(jdk_library, 32.23KiB)\\n========================================================================================================================\\nFinished generating 'com.sun.istack.istack-commons-tools_tests-tests' in 39.2s.\\n\\nThe build process encountered 5 warnings.\\n\\n[native-image-plugin] Native Image written to: /home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge10/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/3272-ef310029/tests/src/com.sun.istack/istack-commons-tools/4.1.2/build/native/nativeTestCompile\\n\\n> Task :nativeTraceImage\\n\\n> Task :runNativeTraceImage\\n[junit-platform-native] WARNING: -djunit.platform.listeners.uid.tracking.output.dir not specified, trying to find test-ids on default Gradle/Maven locations. As this is a fallback mode, it could take a while. This should only happen if you are running tests executable manually and you didn't pass uid output directory with -djunit.platform.listeners.uid.tracking.output.dir=<path>.\\n[junit-platform-native] WARNING: Using test-ids from default Gradle project location:/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge10/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/3272-ef310029/tests/src/com.sun.istack/istack-commons-tools/4.1.2/build/test-results/test/testlist\\n[junit-platform-native] Running in 'test listener' mode using files matching pattern [junit-platform-unique-ids*] found in folder [/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge10/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/3272-ef310029/tests/src/com.sun.istack/istack-commons-tools/4.1.2/build/test-results/test/testlist] and its subfolders.\\nJUnit Platform on Native Image - report\\n----------------------------------------\\n\\ncom.oracle.svm.core.jdk.resources.MissingResourceRegistrationError: Cannot access resource at path 'parallel-world/sample.txt'.\\n\\nThe matching metadata element in the 'resources' section of 'reachability-metadata.json' is:\\n\\n    {\\n      \\\"glob\\\": \\\"parallel-world/sample.txt\\\"